WEBVTT

00:00:01.330 --> 00:00:03.291
I was born during a war

00:00:03.291 --> 00:00:06.085
that still engulfs
my country, Afghanistan.

00:00:07.128 --> 00:00:10.798
When I was growing up,
violence was all around me.

00:00:11.549 --> 00:00:14.844
I remember sitting
in my living room with my family

00:00:14.886 --> 00:00:19.390
when a distant thud
would jerk us all out of our seats.

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:24.729
As the sound of the rockets
came closer and closer,

00:00:24.729 --> 00:00:27.607
our bodies would coil and freeze.

00:00:28.608 --> 00:00:32.320
My grandmother would take charge
of her terrified flock